    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764670/extras/0a05b3da769871e3b4b9f6c2078a2cff.poster.avif?t=1718030525\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764670/extras/0a05b3da769871e3b4b9f6c2078a2cff.webm?t=1718030525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764670/extras/0a05b3da769871e3b4b9f6c2078a2cff.mp4?t=1718030525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>血腥的每个人 是一款血腥的砍杀游戏，您必须与成群的嗜血恶魔、吸血鬼和其他不死生物战斗，对他们进行时尚的组合攻击，将战场变成一片血腥的混乱。<br><br>主角被称为梦想家，他的体内也流淌着鲜血，但尽管他死了，但他非常灵巧，快速，疯狂，并且和他的亲戚吸血鬼一样嗜血。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764670/extras/3b4815f51d5cf28c18d6e62bdeab7f27.poster.avif?t=1718030525\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764670/extras/3b4815f51d5cf28c18d6e62bdeab7f27.webm?t=1718030525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764670/extras/3b4815f51d5cf28c18d6e62bdeab7f27.mp4?t=1718030525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>在这个世界上大多数好斗的居民中，有最杰出的人物，他们不会介意与你交谈，帮助和给你建议，但即使发生这种情况，这场谈话也只会以血腥结束。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764670/extras/aa4c1dbdcd3024f2b0215609bbcf0133.poster.avif?t=1718030525\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764670/extras/aa4c1dbdcd3024f2b0215609bbcf0133.webm?t=1718030525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764670/extras/aa4c1dbdcd3024f2b0215609bbcf0133.mp4?t=1718030525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>您必须访问的地方居住着不死生物、吸血鬼、哥特式怪物，甚至是疯狂的护士，他们甚至可以为骷髅输血。<br><br>多亏了战斗后获得的鲜血，你可以改变梦想家的形象，赋予他不同的能力，与他的战斗风格相得益彰。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764670/extras/ccbd14e69985abcecd5f3f9ccc7f5bc1.poster.avif?t=1718030525\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764670/extras/ccbd14e69985abcecd5f3f9ccc7f5bc1.webm?t=1718030525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764670/extras/ccbd14e69985abcecd5f3f9ccc7f5bc1.mp4?t=1718030525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>除了鲜血之外，你还必须找出这些嗜血生物的真正幕后黑手，以及是谁将这个世界变成了血腥的每个人。",
